'''Republic mod armor''' was a type of modular armor issued to [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Republic soldier|soldiers]] during both the [[Mandalorian Wars]] and the [[Jedi Civil War]]. The armor was designed to be easily upgradeable to afford great protection, including resistance to [[Mind trick/Legends|mind-affecting]] powers from [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force users]], even as the armor began to age.

While trying to escape [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] and find [[Bastila Shan]], the mind-wiped former [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] found and took a set of this armor that once belonged to [[Elam Mattic]] in a password-rigged chest.

